            <div class="usage-tips">
                <h3>ðŸ’¡ Color Palette Usage Tips</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use 60-30-10 rule: 60% dominant color, 30% secondary, 10% accent</li>
                    <li>Ensure sufficient contrast for accessibility (WCAG 2.1 guidelines)</li>
                    <li>Test palettes across different devices and lighting conditions</li>
                    <li>Consider color psychology and brand personality</li>
                    <li>Create hover states and interactive variations</li>
                    <li>Use gradient combinations for modern, dynamic effects</li>
                    <li>Always provide fallback colors for better browser support</li>
                    <li>Consider colorblind users when choosing color combinations</li>
                </ul>
